g.text: In order to run a SIL simulation with a random cube, set SIL, skip\_cube\_read and
generate\_cube to 1. Otherwise, if you want to manually load the single faces or the whole
cube, use the tools below with generate\_cube set to 0.
Instead, to run a PIL execution avoiding the webcam acquisition, set SIL and
generate\_cube to 0 and skip\_cube\_read to 1: this way you can manually load the cube
At last, to run a PIL execution inclusive of the webcam acquisition, set skip\_cube\_read to
0. In case of difficulties with the acquisition of the colors, you can still use the load
